            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>創見(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2451-TW</a>)24日09:38上漲24元，股價漲停報268.5元，委買13張、委賣755張，成交7,959張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為電腦等數位產品之記憶體擴充卡。電腦週邊產品。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>創見(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2451-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌1.21%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌1.7%，股價波動與大盤表現同步。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-773 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,548 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-2,345 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+24 張</li> <li>融資增減：+9 張</li> <li>融券增減：+15 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
